| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6186 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a7042f5c-c5c0-516f-9888-927f19f6a7dc"
